---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { SITE } from '../consts';
---
<BaseLayout title="Affiliate Disclosure" description="How MoveWell Reviews makes money and why it doesn't affect our reviews.">
  <article class="container legal">
    <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
    <p class="updated">Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</p>

    <p>
      {SITE.name} ({SITE.domain}) is a reader-supported publication. In accordance with the
      Federal Trade Commission's <a href="https://www.ftc.gov/business-guidance/resources/disclosures-101-social-media-influencers" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      Endorsement Guides (16 CFR Part 255)</a>, we disclose the following:
    </p>

    <h2>How we earn money</h2>
    <p>
      Some links on this site are affiliate links. If you click one of these links and make a
      purchase, we may earn a commission at no additional cost to you. {SITE.name} is a
      participant in the Amazon Services LLC Associates Program, an affiliate advertising
      program designed to provide a means for sites to earn advertising fees by advertising and
      linking to Amazon.com. We may also participate in other affiliate programs, including but
      not limited to ShareASale, Impact, and CJ Affiliate, and may work directly with brands in
      the walking pad and recovery equipment space.
    </p>

    <h2>This does not change our opinions</h2>
    <p>
      Our editorial team selects, tests, and rates every product independently of any affiliate
      relationship. We do not accept payment in exchange for a positive review, and manufacturers
      do not get to see or approve a review before it's published. If we recommend something, it's
      because we believe it's genuinely useful — the presence of an affiliate link never changes
      what we say about a product.
    </p>

    <h2>Where you'll see disclosures</h2>
    <p>
      We place a disclosure notice near the top of any page containing affiliate links (reviews,
      "best of" roundups, comparison tables, and buying guides), in addition to this dedicated
      page. Affiliate links are also marked with <code>rel="sponsored"</code> for search engines.
    </p>

    <h2>Product testing</h2>
    <p>
      Where we state that we "tested" a product, see the specific review for our testing
      methodology. We do not fabricate test results, and we do not display product pricing that
      we haven't verified — always check the merchant's site for current, accurate pricing before
      purchasing.
    </p>

    <h2>Questions</h2>
    <p>
      If you have questions about this disclosure, <a href="/contact">contact us</a>.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal { padding: 40px 24px 70px; max-width: 720px; }
  .updated { color: #888; font-size: 0.85rem; }
  h2 { margin-top: 30px; }
</style>
